<l>uḷḷuvaṉ maṉyā ṉuraippa tavartiṟamāl </l>
<l> kaḷḷam piṟavō pacappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I think (of him) and what I speak about is but his excellence still is there sallowness and this is deceitful.</l>
